        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'A holographic image materializes, showing the petite researcher, gazing from across the River Styx years after her death.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 306,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": 200.0,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'The timestamp... doesn\\'t matter anymore. If this message is unlocked, it means my legacy has reached the right hands, regardless of when.', 4: '1', 18: '100015789'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'Well done, Nirvatia. You too, Nirvatia\\'s companion.', 4: '1', 18: '100015790'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'You see the same astonishment on Nirvatia\\'s face as yours. The woman in the recording finishes speaking, offering only the slightest hint of a smile.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'It\\'s not hard to guess your expressions. After all, I hid the clues in a poem that could only be deciphered by working with someone else.', 4: '1', 18: '100015791'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'I didn\\'t do this solely for encryption purposes, but also because of... a childhood passion I finally remembered.', 4: '1', 18: '100015792'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'In an ancient culture, the words for \"poet\" and \"maker\" were one and the same. Forget those stereotypes about scientific researchers.', 4: '1', 18: '100015793'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Nirvatia lets out a soft chuckle beside you, her eyes meeting yours with a warm glow of understanding.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '18', 2: '501281', 3: '10', 4: '160', 5: '-145', 6: '-200'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Nirvatia', 3: 'She was always...', 4: '18', 18: '100015794'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "DialogDisable",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '18', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'In the recording, Lenore takes a deep breath, her expression growing complex.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'What I\\'m about to say should have been said to you in person, but I could never bring myself to speak the words.', 4: '1', 18: '100015795'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'I bear you no resentment, Nirvatia. You were always forthright with me, whether through dissuasion or warning, fulfilling both your professional duty and personal obligation as a fellow researcher.', 4: '1', 18: '100015796'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'In the end, I only blame myself for going too far down these so-called \"shortcuts.\"', 4: '1', 18: '100015797'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'When time was pressing, I\\'d skip some tests, since the performance discrepancies wouldn\\'t be noticeable in the field. When funds were tight, I\\'d divert substandard materials, since no one would investigate if accidents remained contained...', 4: '1', 18: '100015798'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 50,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'To keep going, I told so many lies that sometimes I started believing them myself. Then, an outsider, someone who had supposedly made grave mistakes herself, burst into my life and questioned everything down to its core.', 4: '1', 18: '100015799'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 51,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'What mistake did you really make? You simply asked \"why.\" Since when did that become a crime?', 4: '1', 18: '100015800'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 52,
        "ActionId": 52,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She shakes her head.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 53,
        "ActionId": 53,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'Sometimes, watching you, I\\'d feel a twisted kind of envy. I was jealous that you could pursue something with such burning conviction, as if you had nothing to lose and all bridges behind you already burned.', 4: '1', 18: '100015801'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 54,
        "ActionId": 54,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'But now that I\\'ve reached this point myself, what I feel isn\\'t relief, but regret.', 4: '1', 18: '100015802'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 55,
        "ActionId": 55,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'Unrealized ideas, words left unsaid, hands I never dared to extend...', 4: '1', 18: '100015803'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 56,
        "ActionId": 56,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'Is this the burden you\\'ve been carrying all along, Nirvatia?', 4: '1', 18: '100015804'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 57,
        "ActionId": 57,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Nirvatia stares at the projection in stunned silence. The hologram is just a monologue... it can never hear her answer.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 58,
        "ActionId": 58,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'The pursuit of truth... it\\'s like walking a long road through a rainy night. Even fellow travelers may not have the fortune to walk side by side.', 4: '1', 18: '100015805'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 59,
        "ActionId": 59,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lenore', 3: 'Either way, I must set forth on this path.', 4: '1', 18: '100015806'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 60,
        "ActionId": 60,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
